            <section class="prose">
              <h2>How this credit card payoff calculator works</h2>
              <p>
                This tool simulates your credit card balance month by month. For
                each month it:
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>
                  Computes interest using your APR converted to a monthly rate.
                </li>
                <li>Adds that interest to your balance.</li>
                <li>
                  Subtracts your payment (at least the minimum, plus any extra
